the TCM forum will be held

3
00:00:11,521 --> 00:00:13,561
on the Dragon Boat Festival.

4
00:00:14,200 --> 00:00:15,841
Why don't you and Dad stay at home?

5
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:18,601
We can meet up next time.

