10
00:01:20,641 --> 00:01:21,681
Nice!

11
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:24,601
Very nice!

12
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:32,800
Please.

13
00:01:33,641 --> 00:01:36,001
Heroine, sing us another song.

14
00:01:37,081 --> 00:01:38,081
Let me clap for you.

15
00:01:39,921 --> 00:01:40,921
Please.

16
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:42,440
Okay.

