00:02:21,721 --> 00:02:22,718
♫ With Qingfeng Sword in my hand ♫

20
00:02:22,801 --> 00:02:24,960
♫ Who else can slay
a dragon with one hand? ♫

21
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,641
Mum, what's wrong?

22
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,840
What's going on?

23
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,120
It's nothing.

24
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,755
The medicinal brew just dried up.

25
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,538
The medicinal brew dried up?

26
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,877
I thought Tou Tou was supposed
to keep an eye on it?

27
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,001
Come out.

28
00:02:56,521 --> 00:02:57,521
Meng Meng!

29
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,040
Meng Meng!

30
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:03,918
Meng Meng.

31
00:03:04,001 --> 00:03:05,480
I'm here for you. Don't be scared.

32
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,840
Everything's fine.

33
00:03:15,441 --> 00:03:17,397
Did you guys tell her
to keep an eye on the brew?

34
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,161
She wanted to do it of her own accord.

35
00:03:19,641 --> 00:03:21,721
She was doing great
for the past few days.

36
00:03:22,001 --> 00:03:23,441
Doing great?

37
00:03:24,001 --> 00:03:25,654
A fire almost happened because of her.

38
00:03:26,441 --> 00:03:27,441
Where is she?

39
00:03:30,001 --> 00:03:31,001
Tian Zhen.

40
00:03:32,721 --> 00:03:33,801
Is Tou Tou sleeping?

41
00:03:34,281 --> 00:03:35,499
Tell her to come downstairs.

42
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,918
She's not in the room.

43
00:03:39,001 --> 00:03:40,521
-She's not around?
-Call her.

44
00:03:42,441 --> 00:03:43,358
Maybe she went loitering...

45
00:03:43,441 --> 00:03:44,441
Call her.

46
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,560
That must be Tou Tou.

47
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,519
Hello. We're the management team.

48
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,558
The smoke alarm was sounded.

49
00:03:56,641 --> 00:03:57,641
Did something happen?

50
00:03:58,028 --> 00:03:59,757
It's nothing. We already
dealt with the issue.

51
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,558
Thank you for coming.

52
00:04:00,641 --> 00:04:01,597
We have to inspect the scene

53
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,115
to prevent any potential hazards.

54
00:04:04,721 --> 00:04:05,804
Please come in then.

55
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,280
Sun Tou Tou, where are you?

56
00:04:22,561 --> 00:04:23,357
Hello.

57
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,484
I'm not the phone owner.

58
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,160
Who are you then?

59
00:04:27,641 --> 00:04:28,685
Where's the phone owner?

60
00:04:29,361 --> 00:04:31,144
I'm a security guard of Danguiyuan Villa.

61
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,000
I was patrolling the nearby area

62
00:04:33,361 --> 00:04:34,278
when I saw this phone ringing.

63
00:04:34,361 --> 00:04:35,448
That's why I answered it.

64
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,440
The phone owner is...

65
00:04:38,801 --> 00:04:39,838
I didn't see her.

66
00:04:39,921 --> 00:04:40,961
There's no one here.

67
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,440
There's no one there?

68
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,447
This is bad. She might have
jumped into the lake.

69
00:04:55,081 --> 00:04:56,720
I found her socks here.

70
00:04:57,921 --> 00:04:59,158
I tried to scoop the lake,

71
00:04:59,241 --> 00:05:00,241
but I found nothing.

72
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,361
How deep is this lake?

73
00:05:05,554 --> 00:05:06,753
It's not that deep.

74
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,465
It's not even two meters deep.

75
00:05:08,961 --> 00:05:10,961
But someone drowned here last year.

76
00:05:13,081 --> 00:05:14,361
Is she drunk?

77
00:05:15,081 --> 00:05:16,838
I found several empty beer bottles there.

78
00:05:16,921 --> 00:05:17,921
I'm sure she's drunk.

79
00:05:22,121 --> 00:05:23,241
Let's find her first.

80
00:05:25,521 --> 00:05:26,521
Tian Zhen,

81
00:05:26,921 --> 00:05:27,921
you know how to swim.

82
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,625
Search for her under the lake.

83
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,517
Okay.

84
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,121
I'll check over there then.

85
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,200
Tian Zhen, be careful.

86
00:05:57,361 --> 00:05:58,361
Tian Zhen, be careful.

87
00:05:59,801 --> 00:06:01,149
Make sure your steps are solid.

88
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,438
I found her!

89
00:06:07,521 --> 00:06:08,521
Dad, I found her!

90
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,320
I found her!

91
00:06:10,681 --> 00:06:11,681
Mum!

92
00:06:17,641 --> 00:06:18,641
You want to take

93
00:06:18,921 --> 00:06:20,443
a person like her to the TCM forum?

94
00:06:20,641 --> 00:06:21,880
Do you want everyone

95
00:06:22,121 --> 00:06:23,401
to laugh at us?

96
00:06:23,521 --> 00:06:25,043
You're taking her to the TCM forum?

97
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,200
Are you asking me?

98
00:06:28,241 --> 00:06:29,589
Didn't you read the group chat?

99
00:06:30,961 --> 00:06:32,600
The name list is inside.

100
00:06:32,801 --> 00:06:33,932
Your name is included too.

101
00:06:35,401 --> 00:06:36,440
Can I skip it?

102
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,717
Someone needs to take care of Meng Meng.

103
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,598
No.

104
00:06:38,681 --> 00:06:39,838
This is a valuable chance
for you to learn something.

105
00:06:39,921 --> 00:06:41,278
We should let my seniors

106
00:06:41,361 --> 00:06:42,561
join the forum instead.

107
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,797
I have plenty of chances in the future.

108
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:44,838
No.

109
00:06:44,921 --> 00:06:45,921
You have to go.

110
00:06:46,121 --> 00:06:47,440
But why?

111
00:06:48,081 --> 00:06:50,117
Your great-uncle is the president
of the forum this year.

112
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,480
He designated you to go.

113
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,480
Fine then.

114
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,558
Great-uncle is amazing indeed.

115
00:06:55,641 --> 00:06:57,038
No one can defy the words of a fellow.

116
00:06:57,121 --> 00:06:58,904
However, I have to take
Meng Meng with me.

117
00:07:00,121 --> 00:07:01,165
You're taking her along?

118
00:07:02,361 --> 00:07:03,344
That won't do.

119
00:07:03,427 --> 00:07:06,318
We've already told the organisers
about the number of people we'll bring.

120
00:07:06,401 --> 00:07:08,097
We cannot add or subtract them at will.

121
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,200
Mum,

122
00:07:09,361 --> 00:07:10,438
what if Meng Meng wakes up

123
00:07:10,521 --> 00:07:12,117
and causes a ruckus in the middle
of the night after my departure?

124
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,280
Will you coax her then?

125
00:07:18,641 --> 00:07:19,641
What should we do then?

126
00:07:20,943 --> 00:07:21,943
Why don't we

127
00:07:22,361 --> 00:07:23,681
tell Meng Meng's mother

128
00:07:23,886 --> 00:07:24,926
to take her home?

129
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,301
I'll discuss it with Li Quan.

130
00:07:28,401 --> 00:07:29,401
He can stay.

131
00:07:29,961 --> 00:07:30,917
We're very close to each other.

132
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,348
I'm sure he'll be fine with it.

133
00:07:34,038 --> 00:07:35,908
Check on Tou Tou when
you go upstairs later.

134
00:07:36,081 --> 00:07:37,200
She just threw up.

135
00:07:37,961 --> 00:07:40,353
Make sure she doesn't have
anything stuck in her throat.

136
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,480
I'll go.

137
00:07:41,801 --> 00:07:43,801
I'm not sleeping tonight.
I'll look after them.

138
00:07:56,535 --> 00:07:58,438
Mum, we can talk tomorrow.

139
00:07:58,521 --> 00:07:59,517
You've been busy all night.

140
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,600
Get back to sleep.

141
00:08:04,081 --> 00:08:05,521
Where did you go tonight?

142
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,801
I didn't go anywhere.

143
00:08:09,121 --> 00:08:10,121
Look into my eyes.

144
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:19,241
You went drinking with Sun Tou Tou, huh?

145
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,440
Nope.

146
00:08:22,081 --> 00:08:23,081
Really?

147
00:08:32,761 --> 00:08:35,640
You're lucky that
nothing happened to her today.

148
00:08:36,881 --> 00:08:38,273
If something does happen to her,

149
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,640
we'll be

150
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:43,080
imprisoned for it.

151
00:08:51,361 --> 00:08:52,840
I know you don't like her.

152
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,825
Even so, you mustn't harm her.

153
00:08:55,881 --> 00:08:57,921
You need to keep your conscience clear.

154
00:08:58,761 --> 00:09:00,158
Mum, we just had a few drinks.

155
00:09:00,241 --> 00:09:02,121
I never expected her
to fall into the lake.

156
00:09:04,201 --> 00:09:06,278
Now, you're so close to her
that you can drink together with her

157
00:09:06,361 --> 00:09:08,241
and call her your buddy, huh?

158
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,640
Tian Zhen, listen carefully.

159
00:09:13,201 --> 00:09:15,557
Whether Sun Tou Tou
can stay in this family or not

160
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,718
depends on

161
00:09:16,801 --> 00:09:18,561
her performance.

162
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,214
But it's different for you.

163
00:09:21,201 --> 00:09:23,640
You have to establish
your own family in the future.

164
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,197
If your father hears about this,

165
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,541
he'll chase you out of the family
before Sun Tou Tou.

166
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,640
If you don't adjust your state of mind

167
00:09:34,881 --> 00:09:36,280
and co-exist with her,

168
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,943
I may not be able to
defend you next time.

169
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,799
Mum,

170
00:09:44,882 --> 00:09:46,077
I know my fault now.

171
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,201
I won't do it again.

172
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,080
Again?

173
00:09:50,708 --> 00:09:51,752
What are you smiling at?

174
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,600
Mum, I won't do it again.

175
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:58,160
Stay away from her.

176
00:10:05,561 --> 00:10:06,881
And, stay away

177
00:10:07,761 --> 00:10:09,160
from that girl as well.

178
00:10:10,201 --> 00:10:12,201
This is a serious warning.

179
00:10:24,761 --> 00:10:25,761
Mum, what do you want?

180
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,637
Tend to your own needs.

181
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,720
Come.

182
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:32,160
Tian Zhen.

183
00:10:32,881 --> 00:10:33,881
Have a herbal tea egg.

184
00:10:35,001 --> 00:10:36,241
I feel like I'm dying.

185
00:10:39,001 --> 00:10:40,001
This feels terrible.

186
00:10:41,321 --> 00:10:42,757
I'm going to die.

187
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,877
What nonsense are you uttering
this early in the morning?

188
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,997
I feel terrible.

189
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,689
I feel cold and hot at the same time.

190
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,881
Your pulse is tender and weak.

191
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,874
Seems like you need to
take Chinese medicine.

192
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:01,839
No way.

193
00:11:01,922 --> 00:11:03,561
I'll be fine after a few days.

194
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,720
I'm going to sleep.

195
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,400
Finish the hot congee.

196
00:11:12,761 --> 00:11:13,761
Avoid other food.

197
00:11:15,321 --> 00:11:16,557
Must I have it by itself?

198
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:18,160
-Yes.
-Without anything else?

199
00:11:18,761 --> 00:11:19,761
But...

200
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,907
Who did you drink
together with last night?

201
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:41,160
I

202
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,976
drank alone.

203
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:48,080
You finished eight bottles of beer

204
00:11:48,761 --> 00:11:50,881
and an entire bottle of Shaoxing wine?

205
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,520
Shaoxing wine?

206
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,960
Wait.

207
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,918
You said this yourself.

208
00:11:59,001 --> 00:12:00,757
To invite the moon I raise my cup.

209
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,637
We're three, as my shadow shows up.

210
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:05,557
I just wanted to see

211
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:07,678
how it became three people.

212
00:12:07,761 --> 00:12:09,321
I was just curious about that.

213
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:11,361
I was just wondering

214
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,197
how it became three people.

215
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,881
It was pretty strange to me.

216
00:12:16,201 --> 00:12:17,441
You drank

217
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,101
all those liquor by yourself?

218
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:24,080
Everybody knows that
I can hold my liquor well.

219
00:12:24,241 --> 00:12:26,678
I got drunk because I consumed
different types of alcohol.

220
00:12:26,761 --> 00:12:29,637
If you mix beer with rice wine, it'll...

221
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,720
Tou Tou,

222
00:12:31,201 --> 00:12:33,400
you mustn't lie in front of Master.

223
00:12:36,441 --> 00:12:37,720
You must be honest.

224
00:12:38,881 --> 00:12:40,718
If I discover that you're lying,

225
00:12:40,801 --> 00:12:42,160
I'll punish you severely.

226
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,025
Are you going to chase me out?

227
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:00,361
I will face the music alone.

228
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:02,201
I drank by myself.

229
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:04,280
It has nothing to do with other people.

230
00:13:09,441 --> 00:13:10,441
Do not do it again.

231
00:13:12,321 --> 00:13:14,626
Copy Virtue of A Great Physician
for the entire month.

232
00:13:16,881 --> 00:13:20,400
You wanted to tend to
Meng Meng's medicine yourself.

233
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,206
In the end, you failed your mission.

234
00:13:22,441 --> 00:13:23,918
Not only did you break your promise
and behave irresponsibly,

235
00:13:24,001 --> 00:13:26,321
but you also wasted Meng Meng's medicine.

236
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:29,134
Meng Meng hasn't even taken
her medicine yet today.

237
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:32,640
Meng Meng,

238
00:13:32,761 --> 00:13:33,761
I'm sorry.

239
00:13:34,160 --> 00:13:37,201
Last night was an accident.

240
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:38,718
It definitely won't happen again.

241
00:13:38,801 --> 00:13:40,678
Look at me.

242
00:13:40,761 --> 00:13:41,997
I've suffered my retribution.

243
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,441
Will you please forgive me?

244
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,001
Meng Meng forgave me.

245
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:49,564
I can't take it anymore.

246
00:13:50,561 --> 00:13:51,801
Can I take a nap?

247
00:13:52,001 --> 00:13:53,001
Show me your hand.

248
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,317
Measure your right pulse
with your left hand.

249
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:58,238
Nephew,

250
00:13:58,321 --> 00:13:59,321
do you know

251
00:13:59,761 --> 00:14:00,679
what situation we're in?

252
00:14:00,762 --> 00:14:03,400
You're still trying to train me here?

253
00:14:04,561 --> 00:14:06,561
-Goodness.
-Practice makes perfect.

254
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:08,574
Rome wasn't built in a day.

255
00:14:08,761 --> 00:14:11,201
Feel your beating pulse.

256
00:14:11,561 --> 00:14:12,692
Did you detect any changes

257
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,080
besides the beating?

258
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,877
Wait.

259
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,520
It isn't beating anymore.

260
00:14:25,321 --> 00:14:26,321
Wait!

261
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:28,480
Why isn't it beating anymore?

262
00:14:28,761 --> 00:14:29,838
What's going on?

263
00:14:29,921 --> 00:14:31,118
Examine me!

264
00:14:31,201 --> 00:14:31,998
Examine me!

265
00:14:32,081 --> 00:14:34,201
Am I dying?

266
00:14:34,520 --> 00:14:35,520
-Here.
-Niece-in-law!

267
00:14:35,681 --> 00:14:36,598
Finish this.

268
00:14:36,681 --> 00:14:37,761
What is this?

269
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,321
Examine my pulse!

270
00:14:39,881 --> 00:14:41,640
Finish the Fukangling.

271
00:14:42,761 --> 00:14:43,761
Take it while it's hot.

272
00:14:46,201 --> 00:14:47,201
This is amulet water?

273
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,118
Will I die?

274
00:14:50,201 --> 00:14:52,080
Must I take amulet water now?

275
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:53,520
It's not amulet water.

276
00:14:53,881 --> 00:14:54,881
It's a health drink.

277
00:14:56,321 --> 00:14:58,080
What exactly is it?

278
00:14:59,201 --> 00:15:00,361
It's spicy hot pot soup.

279
00:15:03,561 --> 00:15:04,438
That's impossible.

280
00:15:04,521 --> 00:15:05,561
You lied to me.

281
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,997
It doesn't taste like hot pot at all.

282
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,733
It tastes like Chinese medicine to me.

283
00:15:08,881 --> 00:15:11,997
It's made with medicinal ingredients
you can find in the kitchen.

284
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:15,437
For example, dried ginger,
dried orange peel,

285
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:16,561
red dates, and so on.

286
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:17,678
It dispels coldness.

287
00:15:17,761 --> 00:15:19,480
You got drunk last night.

288
00:15:20,441 --> 00:15:21,920
Your spleen and stomach are heaty.

289
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,238
Your body was heaty too.

290
00:15:23,321 --> 00:15:24,640
When you jumped into the lake,

291
00:15:25,761 --> 00:15:27,001
the water was cold.

292
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:29,720
Coldness is born below the feet.

293
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,197
Heat and coldness started
fighting in your middle energizer,

294
00:15:32,280 --> 00:15:33,478
which consists of your spleen

295
00:15:33,561 --> 00:15:34,561
and stomach.

296
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:36,640
Essentially, it's your stomach.

297
00:15:37,201 --> 00:15:38,119
Actually, your body

298
00:15:38,202 --> 00:15:40,001
was expelling sweat automatically.

299
00:15:40,441 --> 00:15:42,317
It's stated clearly within
Yellow Emperor's Inner Classic,

300
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:43,881
Discourse on Heat.

301
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:46,160
Now, as for heat diseases,

302
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:49,201
they all are of the type
"harm caused by cold".

303
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:51,718
No matter if your body is heaty

304
00:15:51,801 --> 00:15:53,520
or if you have diarrhoea,

305
00:15:53,881 --> 00:15:56,080
as long as it's not food poisoning,

306
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:58,520
it's mostly caused by coldness.

307
00:15:59,321 --> 00:16:00,960
Let me give you an example.

308
00:16:01,321 --> 00:16:02,877
For example, the doors
and windows in our house

309
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:03,918
are closed.

310
00:16:04,001 --> 00:16:05,520
Nothing can get out of the house.

311
00:16:05,778 --> 00:16:06,778
What should we do then?

312
00:16:06,881 --> 00:16:08,201
I'll open a window.

313
00:16:09,321 --> 00:16:12,080
We can take pungent
and warm-natured drugs

314
00:16:12,321 --> 00:16:15,640
so that our body will expel
the coldness automatically.

315
00:16:16,201 --> 00:16:17,593
Our bodies will recover by then.

316
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:21,520
You said this too.

317
00:16:22,649 --> 00:16:24,184
When joy, anger, sorrow, and pleasure
have not yet arisen,

318
00:16:24,267 --> 00:16:25,451
it is called "moderate".

319
00:16:25,561 --> 00:16:28,840
When they arise to their appropriate
levels, it is called "harmony".

320
00:16:29,321 --> 00:16:32,077
That means if we stick to a diet

321
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,317
and adopt a healthy lifestyle,

322
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,239
we won't

323
00:16:34,322 --> 00:16:35,400
fall sick.

324
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:36,757
If we do fall sick,

325
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:37,997
we just need to overcompensate for it.

326
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:38,798
This way,

327
00:16:38,881 --> 00:16:40,229
we'll recover from our illness.

328
00:16:41,001 --> 00:16:42,045
Was that what you meant?

329
00:16:42,201 --> 00:16:43,881
Yes. Finish it while it's hot.

330
00:16:54,001 --> 00:16:55,520
No, I need to take a nap.

331
00:17:01,881 --> 00:17:03,360
You don't even let me take Shumai.

332
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:07,081
She's a promising student.

333
00:17:19,760 --> 00:17:21,152
Look at your so-called good son!

334
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:27,880
Who said girls were inferior to guys?

335
00:17:29,321 --> 00:17:30,998
I will hand over my position
as the leader of the sect

336
00:17:31,081 --> 00:17:32,168
to Tou Tou in the future.

337
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:34,441
Look at that son of yours.

338
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,238
No matter if it's courage or knowledge,

339
00:17:36,321 --> 00:17:37,721
he's no match

340
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,358
for a parent less child

341
00:17:39,441 --> 00:17:40,801
who wasn't even educated.

342
00:17:41,280 --> 00:17:42,561
He's not ready at all!

343
00:17:46,760 --> 00:17:47,878
You want me to chase Tou Tou
out of the house?

344
00:17:47,961 --> 00:17:48,961
In your dreams.

345
00:17:51,201 --> 00:17:52,561
If he does this again,

346
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:53,518
I'll chase him out

347
00:17:53,601 --> 00:17:54,601
without any mercy!

348
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:33,760
What a shame.

349
00:18:34,441 --> 00:18:36,760
The 30-year-old Nu Er Hong wine
had gone to waste.

350
00:18:38,561 --> 00:18:40,120
It would've been nourishing

351
00:18:40,921 --> 00:18:43,081
for the little girl

352
00:18:43,441 --> 00:18:45,201
if she took it moderately.

353
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:48,437
If my foolish grandson

354
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:49,520
was out to harm her,

355
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:51,758
he didn't need to resort to
using such valuable liquor.

356
00:18:51,841 --> 00:18:52,998
He could've gotten a random
bottle of liquor

357
00:18:53,081 --> 00:18:54,601
downstairs.

358
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:00,760
I'm being harsh again.

359
00:19:01,197 --> 00:19:02,448
I will reflect upon my actions.

360
00:19:02,531 --> 00:19:03,879
I will reflect upon my actions.

