-Are you busy?

375
00:19:45,561 --> 00:19:47,077
-Resume your work.
-Let me get you a drink.

376
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,552
It's fine. I can do that myself.

377
00:19:49,321 --> 00:19:51,197
Are you two here to get a diagnosis?

378
00:19:51,280 --> 00:19:52,797
Or are you guys to seek other treatments?

379
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:53,598
We're not here to seek physicians.

380
00:19:53,681 --> 00:19:54,437
