-Dad? Mum?

383
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:00,880
Quan.

384
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:02,598
-Son.
-What are you two doing here?

385
00:20:02,681 --> 00:20:03,961
We're here to visit you.

386
00:20:05,201 --> 00:20:06,481
This place is great.

387
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,040
This is great.

388
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:10,152
The environment here is so nice.

389
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,640
Mr Wu,

390
00:20:11,921 --> 00:20:13,000
thank you

391
00:20:13,201 --> 00:20:14,921
for helping Quan to get a job.

392
00:20:15,801 --> 00:20:17,520
Thank you so much.

393
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:18,797
His father and I

394
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:19,719
