to provide for the family in the future.

397
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,077
-Your kid is pretty good.
-Thank you.

398
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:26,721
Thank you for your help.

399
00:20:26,961 --> 00:20:28,077
What are you doing?

400
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,321
You must accept this.

401
00:20:31,321 --> 00:20:32,838
This is for Professor Ren.

402
00:20:32,921 --> 00:20:33,921
This is for you.

403
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,957
One of you helped our child

404
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:36,918
to get a job

405
00:20:37,001 --> 00:20:38,801
while the other is our child's superior.

406
00:20:38,961 --> 00:20:40,317
Both of you are our benefactors.

407
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:41,400
Have a seat.

408
00:20:42,681 --> 00:20:43,599
We were just

409
