fated to meet.

410
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:47,197
I cannot accept your gifts.

411
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:48,358
No. Mr Wu,

412
00:20:48,441 --> 00:20:49,797
you have to accept this.

413
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:51,801
This is just a token of our appreciation.

414
00:20:51,921 --> 00:20:54,921
To you, it might be just
lifting a finger.

415
00:20:55,081 --> 00:20:56,317
However, to our family,

416
00:20:56,400 --> 00:20:58,760
it's a debt of gratitude
