422
00:21:08,321 --> 00:21:11,321
We're very thankful that
the medical centre could help Quan

423
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:13,282
to set his household register here.

424
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:26,760
What about this?

425
00:21:27,801 --> 00:21:28,838
I'll accept your gifts

426
00:21:28,921 --> 00:21:31,081
this time.

427
00:21:31,921 --> 00:21:34,160
But you must never bring them again,

428
00:21:34,441 --> 00:21:35,441
