to visit Jiangzhou.

436
00:21:50,321 --> 00:21:52,040
You should take them around.

437
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:55,238
-Okay.
-Please visit the city.

438
00:21:55,321 --> 00:21:56,321
Thank you.

439
00:21:57,280 --> 00:21:59,020
Don't worry. Your child
is under my care.

440
00:21:59,561 --> 00:22:01,040
Okay. Thank you.

441
00:22:12,721 --> 00:22:14,156
You should break the news to him.

442
00:22:14,441 --> 00:22:15,838
You should do it.

443
00:22:15,921 --> 00:22:17,197
How can I do it?

444
00:22:17,280 --> 00:22:18,280
This matter is too...

445
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:19,718
He's our son. What are you afraid of?

446
00:22:19,801 --> 00:22:20,801
What am I afraid of?

447
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:21,998
Look at what you're saying.

448
00:22:22,081 --> 00:22:23,081
Mum,

449
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:25,238
I thought I told you guys not to come?

450
00:22:25,321 --> 00:22:26,998
Why did you guys appear out of the blue?

451
00:22:27,081 --> 00:22:28,957
You said you'd be busy
during the Dragon Boat Festival, right?

452
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:31,000
That's why we came here earlier.

453
00:22:31,560 --> 00:22:32,358
Okay then.

454
00:22:32,441 --> 00:22:33,638
You and Dad can wait here.

455
00:22:33,721 --> 00:22:35,118
I'll get changed and take you guys out.

456
00:22:35,201 --> 00:22:36,201
No need for that.

457
00:22:36,561 --> 00:22:38,040
You don't need to keep us company.

458
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,943
We'll leave after delivering our message.

459
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,640
Please go ahead.

460
00:22:44,081 --> 00:22:45,081
Quan,

461
00:22:45,921 --> 00:22:47,240
tell me something.

462
00:22:47,561 --> 00:22:50,481
How much do you earn per month?

463
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:53,077
Mum,

464
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:54,508
I started working not long ago.

465
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:56,760
I don't earn that much.

466
00:22:57,201 --> 00:22:58,984
That's why I don't have a lot of savings.

467
00:23:00,321 --> 00:23:01,321
Yeah, I guess so.

468
00:23:03,321 --> 00:23:04,321
Mum, what's the matter?

469
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:06,783
Just tell me if you're having any issues.

470
00:23:06,961 --> 00:23:08,797
You're talking to your own child,
you know?

471
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,681
There's no need to beat around the bush.

472
00:23:10,801 --> 00:23:13,236
Just break the news to him.
There's no need to be scared.

473
00:23:14,040 --> 00:23:16,321
Do you have 20,000 yuan on you?

474
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:19,601
I plan

475
00:23:19,921 --> 00:23:21,530
to breed some lobster fry in our pond

476
00:23:21,760 --> 00:23:23,674
so that we can make some money
during winter.

477
00:23:24,784 --> 00:23:25,784
Quan,

478
00:23:25,961 --> 00:23:26,961
it's like this.

479
00:23:27,561 --> 00:23:29,077
There was a cold spell
during late spring.

480
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:31,118
Half of our fry were dead.

481
00:23:31,201 --> 00:23:32,723
Our investment went down the drain.

482
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,718
Your younger brother will be attending

483
00:23:34,801 --> 00:23:36,601
junior high this year.

484
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:38,321
We need to support him too.

485
00:23:39,961 --> 00:23:40,961
Mum,

486
00:23:41,681 --> 00:23:42,681
I understand now.

487
00:23:43,280 --> 00:23:44,280
Dad,

488
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,478
I'll save up all the money I earn

489
00:23:46,561 --> 00:23:47,605
