00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:11,640
Return to work.

504
00:24:11,801 --> 00:24:12,801
Everything's fine.

505
00:24:13,280 --> 00:24:14,681
Don't apply for leave, okay?

506
00:24:15,681 --> 00:24:16,681
Let's go.

507
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:18,118
Let's leave now.

508
00:24:18,201 --> 00:24:19,118
-Wait.
-Hurry.

509
00:24:19,201 --> 00:24:19,957
See you.

510
00:24:20,040 --> 00:24:21,197
Don't apply for leave, okay?

511
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:22,478
If not, they'll deduct your wage.

512
00:24:22,561 --> 00:24:24,317
Wait, we should take something
since we're already here.

513
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,520
-Let's go.
-Mum.

514
00:24:25,681 --> 00:24:26,677
Aren't you guys going to
spend the night here?

515
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:28,561
No. We don't want to waste money.

516
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:29,557
See you.

517
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:31,280
-But he...
-Let's go.

518
00:24:31,681 --> 00:24:32,718
-Goodness.
-We should at least get money from him.

519
00:24:32,801 --> 00:24:33,639
What are you saying?

520
00:24:33,722 --> 00:24:35,679
We can figure something out
when we head back.

521
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:02,520
Tian Zhen.

522
00:25:03,921 --> 00:25:05,118
-Which car am I taking?
-Sorry.

523
00:25:05,201 --> 00:25:06,518
I forgot to tell you.

524
00:25:06,601 --> 00:25:07,681
You see, it's like this.

525
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,677
If I go alone,

526
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:10,599
Meng Meng will be alone.

527
00:25:10,682 --> 00:25:11,987
Everyone will worry about her.

528
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:13,160
What about this?

529
00:25:13,423 --> 00:25:15,998
We'll have plenty of chances in the
future. You can go next time.

530
00:25:16,081 --> 00:25:17,520
I'm truly sorry about this.

531
00:25:17,729 --> 00:25:18,718
I forgot about it.

532
00:25:18,801 --> 00:25:19,961
-Okay.
