540
00:25:37,040 --> 00:25:38,345
Can't I get myself a follower?

541
00:25:39,441 --> 00:25:40,441
Come on. Let's go.

542
00:25:43,120 --> 00:25:44,120
Let's go.

543
00:25:44,441 --> 00:25:45,441
Let's go.

544
00:25:59,441 --> 00:26:00,441
Mr Wu,

545
00:26:01,801 --> 00:26:02,801
thank you.

546
00:26:06,801 --> 00:26:07,801
My child,

547
00:26:09,040 --> 00:26:10,040
you remind me

548
00:26:11,441 --> 00:26:13,640
of my younger days.

549
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:22,686
(30 years ago)

550
00:26:23,028 --> 00:26:23,957
Ling Ian.

551
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,400
Shan Dao, you're here too?

