with all the cumbersome matters.

612
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:47,681
Good job.

613
00:29:47,961 --> 00:29:48,961
Xin Zheng,

614
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,441
your apprentice class

615
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:53,040
