648
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:11,640
When my father was still around,

649
00:31:11,921 --> 00:31:12,921
I think...

650
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:15,280
It should be her grandmother.

651
00:31:16,520 --> 00:31:17,359
That's right.

652
00:31:17,442 --> 00:31:18,840
Your grandmother

653
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:21,801
