00:31:56,036 --> 00:31:57,961
Over here.
Sit here.

667
00:32:00,215 --> 00:32:01,197
See you.

668
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:02,280
She's coming.

669
00:32:03,561 --> 00:32:05,400
Come here.
Come.

