684
00:32:29,081 --> 00:32:30,077
I need to keep her company.

685
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,421
You guys can enjoy your meal.

686
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,681
What patient?

687
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:35,441
She must be your girlfriend.

688
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:38,599
-Take her here too.
-That's not it.

689
00:32:39,107 --> 00:32:40,880
Secretary Qian, get us two more chairs.

690
00:32:41,561 --> 00:32:43,718
