for my juniors.

699
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:04,880
Sit properly.

700
00:33:20,280 --> 00:33:21,280
Thank you.

701
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:51,227
Peng Shi Yan?

702
00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:52,310
Peng Shi Yan.

703
00:33:53,801 --> 00:33:55,358
What are you doing here?

704
00:33:55,441 --> 00:33:57,094
-Why can't I be here?
-What's going on?

705
00:33:57,961 --> 00:33:58,961
Is she your friend?

706
00:34:00,040 --> 00:34:01,040
Dormmate!

707
00:34:02,280 --> 00:34:03,640
What are you doing here?

708
00:34:04,321 --> 00:34:05,317
Wait.

709
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:07,227
How come the two of you
came here together?

710
00:34:08,450 --> 00:34:09,438
She brought me along.

711
00:34:09,521 --> 00:34:10,521
I didn't.

712
00:34:11,441 --> 00:34:12,441
You're something else.

713
00:34:16,921 --> 00:34:17,961
Take me with you.

714
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,198
A spy like me

715
00:34:20,281 --> 00:34:23,238
needs to head to the enemy's nest
to eradicate them once and for all.

716
00:34:23,921 --> 00:34:24,958
Take me with you.

717
00:34:25,041 --> 00:34:25,839
You're a renowned figure.

718
00:34:25,922 --> 00:34:27,575
You need to have a servant beside you.

719
00:34:28,160 --> 00:34:29,360
Besides,

720
00:34:29,761 --> 00:34:31,457
the mountain path is rugged and uneven.

721
00:34:31,961 --> 00:34:33,077
I checked the schedule too.

722
00:34:33,160 --> 00:34:34,717
We have to gather mugwort
before dawn on the second day.

723
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:36,037
I'm sure you'll depart at night.

724
00:34:36,120 --> 00:34:37,557
What if you encounter a bear

725
00:34:37,640 --> 00:34:39,441
or a robber? It'll be dangerous.

726
00:34:40,281 --> 00:34:41,360
Most importantly,

727
00:34:42,970 --> 00:34:43,914
it's a long journey.

728
00:34:43,997 --> 00:34:46,397
You need a second driver somehow.

729
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:12,080
Thanks.

730
00:35:13,721 --> 00:35:14,761
Give me some time.

731
00:35:15,080 --> 00:35:16,820
You can drive once I'm done throwing up.

732
00:35:19,201 --> 00:35:20,984
You'll drive once
you're done throwing up.

733
00:35:24,160 --> 00:35:25,160
Why?

734
00:35:25,836 --> 00:35:26,836
I have motion sickness.

735
00:35:27,001 --> 00:35:28,158
You won't get that when you drive.

736
00:35:28,241 --> 00:35:30,080
Only passengers will get that.

737
00:35:31,761 --> 00:35:32,761
