when you drank water?

745
00:35:45,721 --> 00:35:48,156
Who kept your bottle for you
once you were done drinking?

746
00:35:48,241 --> 00:35:49,676
I did my job as your co-driver...

747
00:36:08,921 --> 00:36:10,269
