748
00:36:17,281 --> 00:36:18,681
Wait for me!

749
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,120
Wait for me!

750
00:36:24,001 --> 00:36:25,001
I...

751
00:36:26,241 --> 00:36:27,241
I...

752
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:32,721
Peng Shi Yan,

753
00:36:33,281 --> 00:36:34,560
let me put it this way.

754
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:36,761
You should be grateful

755
00:36:37,001 --> 00:36:38,398
that Roubecca didn't leave you

756
00:36:38,481 --> 00:36:39,318
in the wilderness

757
00:36:39,401 --> 00:36:40,557
alone.

758
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:42,598
You have to be content, you know?

759
00:36:42,681 --> 00:36:43,878
She wanted to leave me behind.

760
00:36:43,961 --> 00:36:45,281
But I was stubborn.

761
00:37:19,481 --> 00:37:20,640
Intellectual my foot!

762
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:23,678
She forgot to fill up her gas tank
before setting off to this place.

763
00:37:23,761 --> 00:37:25,237
-Drive my car there.
-She would've still been stuck

764
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:26,238
on the road asking for help

765
00:37:26,321 --> 00:37:27,997
if it weren't for me.

766
00:37:28,080 --> 00:37:29,080
Don't you think so?

767
00:37:29,241 --> 00:37:30,441
She's leaving angrily.

768
00:37:31,041 --> 00:37:32,441
-Professor Ren.
-Let's go.

769
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,560
Okay.

770
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:37,681
Peng Shi Yan was abandoned by
Roubecca on the road.

771
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:44,800
Master,

772
00:37:45,001 --> 00:37:46,158
I thought we were holding a meeting?

773
00:37:46,241 --> 00:37:47,118
Why are we

774
00:37:47,201 --> 00:37:48,721
harvesting mugwort now?

775
00:37:49,721 --> 00:37:52,400
Why aren't you calling me
your nephew today?

776
00:37:56,521 --> 00:37:58,043
Yesterday, together with my senior,

777
00:37:58,761 --> 00:38:00,640
which was Fellow Zhang,

778
00:38:01,320 --> 00:38:02,320
we had

779
00:38:02,921 --> 00:38:04,961
a long chat.

780
00:38:05,560 --> 00:38:08,241
He told me that if I truly
wanted to learn,

781
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:10,521
I need to have a respectful heart.

782
00:38:11,256 --> 00:38:12,198
That means

783
00:38:12,281 --> 00:38:14,800
I have to respect my teachers
from the bottom of my heart.

784
00:38:15,001 --> 00:38:16,838
It's not like I called you nephew

785
00:38:16,921 --> 00:38:17,718
because I disrespected you.

786
00:38:17,801 --> 00:38:19,438
We're relatives, right?

787
00:38:19,521 --> 00:38:21,317
I called you Nephew because
I thought it sounded endearing.

788
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,481
And, he said

789
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:27,160
inheritance is just like a river
flowing into the sea.

790
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:29,557
Water flows downwards.

791
00:38:29,640 --> 00:38:31,921
Once I have a respectful heart,

792
00:38:32,281 --> 00:38:34,477
I can learn and absorb
my master's teaching

793
00:38:34,560 --> 00:38:35,678
just like how the sea
accommodates the rivers

794
00:38:35,761 --> 00:38:37,281
by absorbing them.

795
00:38:37,674 --> 00:38:38,674
He even said

796
00:38:38,761 --> 00:38:41,160
there are 64 hexagrams
in the Book of Changes.

797
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:44,158
Every hexagram has its pros and cons.

798
00:38:44,241 --> 00:38:45,921
There are both sides to them.

799
00:38:46,241 --> 00:38:47,557
However, there's only one thing

800
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:48,814
that doesn't have any cons.

801
00:38:49,668 --> 00:38:50,668
That is...

802
00:38:50,842 --> 00:38:51,842
Modesty.

803
00:38:53,157 --> 00:38:53,958
That's right.

804
00:38:54,041 --> 00:38:55,080
As the saying goes,

805
00:38:55,560 --> 00:38:56,691
pride comes before a fall.

806
00:38:57,481 --> 00:38:58,997
Yes. That's it.

807
00:38:59,080 --> 00:39:00,557
Anyway, Fellow Zhang told me

808
00:39:00,640 --> 00:39:03,797
to obey my mentor
and be respectful to them.

809
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:04,880
That's right.

810
00:39:11,721 --> 00:39:13,918
Tou Tou, you've improved upon
two points today.

811
00:39:14,001 --> 00:39:16,961
First, you're able to
take other people's advice.

812
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:18,961
Second, you know
how to raise questions now.

813
00:39:19,721 --> 00:39:20,721
Very good.

814
00:39:22,514 --> 00:39:24,674
Actually, we're

815
00:39:25,441 --> 00:39:26,721
stagnant most of the time.

816
00:39:27,001 --> 00:39:30,001
The Dragon Boat Festival coincides
with the activation of Yang energy.

817
00:39:30,761 --> 00:39:32,979
When you stay active,
it activates your Yang energy.

818
00:39:33,241 --> 00:39:35,077
And, mugwort helps
generate warmer Yang energy.

819
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:36,481
That's why today,

820
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:39,237
