to generate warmer Yang energy.

821
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:41,712
How does harvesting mugwort
generate warmer Yang energy?

822
00:39:42,160 --> 00:39:44,481
To put it accurately, mugwort
dredges our meridians.

823
00:39:44,721 --> 00:39:47,241
In the past, when our predecessors
went hunting,

824
00:39:47,481 --> 00:39:49,521
they'd be gone for a few days.

825
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,237
They didn't bring any water with them.

826
00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:52,638
They only brought mugwort with them.

827
00:39:52,721 --> 00:39:53,639
When they were thirsty,

828
00:39:53,722 --> 00:39:55,800
they would dig a hole

829
00:39:56,160 --> 00:39:57,204
and ignite some mugwort.

830
00:39:57,560 --> 00:40:01,800
The smoke that was produced by burning
mugwort would flow underground.

831
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:05,041
If they saw smoke on the far side,

832
00:40:05,201 --> 00:40:07,961
it meant that
there was water underground.

833
00:40:09,001 --> 00:40:11,041
During our class, I talked about

834
00:40:11,681 --> 00:40:13,158
how Tao follows the ways of itself.

835
00:40:13,241 --> 00:40:14,958
The ways of Heaven, Earth, and Man

836
00:40:15,041 --> 00:40:16,041
are interconnected.

837
00:40:16,721 --> 00:40:17,721
What is Tao?

838
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:19,761
Tao is regularity.

839
00:40:21,721 --> 00:40:23,120
Mugwort

840
00:40:23,281 --> 00:40:25,880
can dredge the earthly meridians.

841
00:40:26,241 --> 00:40:28,521
It has the same effect on our body.

842
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:32,201
It can overcome resistance
and find the cause.

843
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:35,241
In the past,

844
00:40:35,441 --> 00:40:37,360
I thought the heat during moxibustion

845
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:39,077
was the element that cured illnesses.

846
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:41,320
I never expected it to be the smoke.

847
00:40:41,721 --> 00:40:44,281
No matter if it's the heat or smoke,

848
00:40:45,441 --> 00:40:48,761
it's beneficial to
the patient's recovery.

849
00:40:49,640 --> 00:40:50,858
What does "beneficial" mean?

850
00:40:52,201 --> 00:40:53,462
That means it's good for you.

851
00:40:55,481 --> 00:40:56,638
If mugwort is that good,

852
00:40:56,721 --> 00:40:57,721
I have to harvest

853
00:40:58,080 --> 00:41:00,080
more of them today.

854
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,398
After harvesting them,

855
00:41:01,481 --> 00:41:03,400
you can hang it on your door

856
00:41:03,761 --> 00:41:06,080
or take a bath with it.

857
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:08,560
It's good for your body.

858
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:10,192
It generates warmer Yang energy.

859
00:41:15,241 --> 00:41:16,241
Let's hurry.

860
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:25,298
(Mugwort)

861
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:30,605
(Warms the meridians, stops bleeding,
expels coldness, stops pain, and so on)

862
00:41:30,961 --> 00:41:32,041
This place is amazing.

863
00:41:32,241 --> 00:41:33,118
The weather is great too.

864
00:41:33,201 --> 00:41:34,638
-Okay.
-What do you think that looks like?

865
00:41:34,721 --> 00:41:36,118
-Professor Ren.
-A huge tea plantation.

866
00:41:36,201 --> 00:41:37,201
Professor Ren.

867
00:41:38,241 --> 00:41:39,241
What's the matter?

868
00:41:39,961 --> 00:41:41,598
-I need you to do me a favour.
-What is it?

869
00:41:41,681 --> 00:41:43,320
My daughter is having a high fever.

870
00:41:44,041 --> 00:41:45,317
I don't know

871
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:47,118
if it was because she had something bad

872
00:41:47,201 --> 00:41:47,919
or caught a cold.

873
00:41:48,002 --> 00:41:49,477
I just gave her fever medicine
this morning.

874
00:41:49,560 --> 00:41:50,757
But now, she's feverish again.

875
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:53,557
Professor Ren,
please give her a diagnosis.

876
00:41:53,640 --> 00:41:54,640
Calm down.

877
00:41:55,201 --> 00:41:56,521
Mr Zheng, don't be anxious.

878
00:41:57,681 --> 00:42:00,160
There's no need to be anxious
when your child has a fever.

879
00:42:00,331 --> 00:42:01,158
Look.

880
00:42:01,241 --> 00:42:03,155
We have all the physicians
in the world here.

881
00:42:03,281 --> 00:42:04,281
Yeah, Mr Zheng.

882
00:42:04,640 --> 00:42:07,041
It's common for children to catch a cold

883
00:42:07,241 --> 00:42:08,237
or have a fever.

884
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,958
We TCM practitioners have been
studying this topic

885
00:42:10,041 --> 00:42:11,481
for millenniums.

886
00:42:12,160 --> 00:42:13,552
Let me recommend someone to you.

887
00:42:14,241 --> 00:42:16,241
What about the son
of Professor Ren, Tian Zhen?

888
